<div class="row justify-content-center">
  <div class="col-12 col-lg-8 col-xl-7">
    <div class="card shadow-sm border-0 ticket-form-card">
      <div class="card-body">
        <div class="d-flex justify-content-between align-items-start flex-wrap gap-2 mb-3">
          <div>
            <h1 class="h4 mb-1">Neues Support-Ticket</h1>
            <p class="text-muted small mb-0">
              Schildere dein Anliegen so genau wie m√∂glich ‚Äì Screenshots, Schritte und erwartetes Verhalten helfen enorm.
